&quot;Calvin Ellis Stowe (1802-1886)

Calvin Ellis Stowe was married to Harriet Beecher Stowe (1811-1896), the author of &quot;Uncle Tom's Cabin.&quot; He was an educator and professor of religion and ancient languages. Stowe taught at Dartmouth, Bowdoin, and Andover Theological Seminary. He also wrote several books on the Bible.&quot;

